OL,3,CWhat is the Hillsborough Law?
OL,5,FThe long-awaited bill to create a
OL,6,FHillsborough Law will finally be
OL,7,Fapproved by MPs today, more than three
OL,8,Fdecades since the disaster.
OL,10,FThe law change, officially known as
OL,11,Fthe Public Office (Accountability)
OL,12,FBill, will make it a legal duty for
OL,13,Fpublic officials to act transparently
OL,14,Fwhen investigations and inquiries take
OL,15,Fplace.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
