OL,3,CWhat is the Hillsborough Law?
OL,5,FIt takes its name from the
OL,6,FHillsborough disaster in 1989 when 97
OL,7,FLiverpool fans were killed following a
OL,8,Fcrush at a football stadium in
OL,9,FSheffield during an FA Cup semi-final
OL,10,Fmatch.
OL,12,FFamilies of those killed were forced
OL,13,Fto fight a long campaign to get to the
OL,14,Ftruth behind the disaster, after
OL,15,FLiverpool fans were wrongly blamed for
OL,16,Fwhat happened.
OL,18,FSimilar calls have since been made by
OL,19,Ffamilies affected by other public
OL,20,Fdisasters, including the Manchester
OL,21,FArena bombing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
