OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784107114
OL,3,CWhat is the Hillsborough Law?
OL,5,FWhat is the bill?
OL,7,FThe law will create a legally-
OL,8,Fenforceable "duty of candour" for
OL,9,Fpublic officials to tell the truth to
OL,10,Finquiries and investigations.
OL,12,FPrime minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,13,Fhe was "proud" to bring back the
OL,14,Flegislation, which aims to prevent
OL,15,Fcover-ups and concealment.
OL,17,FThe Hillsborough Law will also ensure
OL,18,Fvictims of disasters or state-related
OL,19,Fdeaths are entitled to parity of legal
OL,20,Frepresentation during inquests and
OL,21,Finquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
