OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784107114
OL,3,CWhat is the Hillsborough Law?
OL,5,FThis will mean that bereaved families
OL,6,Fcan get public funding, just as public
OL,7,Fmoney is used to support Government
OL,8,Fand public authority lawyers.
OL,10,FThe bill was a key promise in Labour's
OL,11,F2024 manifesto, but has been delayed
OL,12,Fover how the measures would apply to
OL,13,Fspies.
OL,15,FThe original proposals gave
OL,16,Fintelligence agencies the right to
OL,17,Fchoose whether to co-operate with
OL,18,Fpublic inquiries, but campaigners
OL,19,Frefused to accept this.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
