OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784107114
OL,3,CWhat is the Hillsborough Law?
OL,5,FFamilies of the 2017 Manchester Arena
OL,6,Fbombing wrote to Starmer in January to
OL,7,Fsay MI5 should not be exempt.
OL,9,FOn Tuesday, 14 July ministers will
OL,10,Famend the Bill to apply its duty of
OL,11,Fcandour to spies, but with a "secure
OL,12,Fprocess" for disclosing information
OL,13,Fthat could affect national security.
OL,15,FThe legislation will still need to go
OL,16,Fthrough the House of Lords.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
