OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784107114
OL,3,CWhat is the Hillsborough Law?
OL,5,FSir Keir said the "landmark law" was
OL,6,F"a tribute to the incredible families
OL,7,Fand campaigners who have spent decades
OL,8,Fand decades fighting to get justice
OL,9,Ffor their loved ones."
OL,11,FHillsborough Law campaigners,
OL,12,Fincluding those whose family members
OL,13,Fwere killed, welcomed the return of
OL,14,Fthe Bill to the Commons.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Charlotte Hennessy,
OL,17,FSue Roberts, Steve Kelly and Margaret
OL,18,FAspinall said: "We have shown that
OL,19,Ftrue power belongs to ordinary people.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
